    "rationale": "All three primary QoIs meet the E/uval < 1.96 acceptance criterion. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed; the Test conditions factor achieves one level below required but is accepted given the standardized ASTM F1717 protocol. The credibility evidence package is deemed sufficient to support the 510(k) submission for the non-cannulated pedicle screw construct.",
